The paper proposes an interactive system for visually exploring the semantic structure of a scientific article, which involves named entity recognition and supervised classifiers. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Deep Learning (cs.DL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
